  <brief_title>A New Non-invasive Marker to Detect Silent Hypoxia in Patients Undergoing Cardiac Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Somatic-to-cerebral Oxygen Saturation Gradient as a Non-invasive Index of Anaerobic Threshold in High-risk Cardiac Surgical Patient</official_title>
  <sponsors>
